Title: Deleting a folder will not delete all files of the contained hosts
Component: wato
State: open
Date: 2015-12-01 21:44:21
Targetversion: future
Class: nastiness

If you delete a single host then via the automation all files belonging
to that host will be deleted (autochecks, counters, etc.). But if you
delete a folder then the files of the contained hosts are *not*
being deleted.
